```
login.invocations:1|c
```

A [`metric` event][docs.metric_event] will be emitted with the following structure:

{% code-tabs %}
{% code-tabs-item title="metric" %}
```javascript
{
  "counter": {
    "name": "login.invocations",
    "val": 1
  }
}
```
